This is essential  for those late nights where you don't remember anything, but you're glad you woke up next to a half eaten sandwich in bed.  It's a submarine sandwich chain so there isn't anything special about the place, but the fact that it's open 24h a day makes it amazing. It's exactly what you would expect from any other Subway you go to, except for the fact that they LOAD IT UP!  The employees are friendly and attentive to your needs. The restaurant is always clean.  If you want sub and don't want to pay bodega prices on a skimpy sandwich, just load up on vegetables and you're good to go.
